Package: hdhomerun-linux-player
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, qml6-module-qtmultimedia, qml6-module-qtquick-controls, qml6-module-qtquick-layouts
Description: HDHomeRun live TV player for Linux
 Native Linux HDHomeRun player composed of a local backend service and a desktop UI.
 This packaging skeleton targets the embedded-playback architecture where the Qt UI
 renders the playback surface in-window and the backend runs in client-managed mode.